I'm wondering how to start my campaign?

Starting a campaign on NewsBreak is quite straightforward! You can head over to admanager.newsbreak.com, enter your email, set a password, and add some business details for verification. Once you're set up, you'll go through three key steps: Campaign, Ad Set, and Ad. For more detailed guidance, you can check out our article on creating your first ad here: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad). Let me know if you need any more help!
